{"tid":1766063,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"黑警戰術更進一步 - 古德明","createTime":"2019-12-02T10:06:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-02T10:34:53.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9c0ec6c23c7a86f32439e265399bb3a1790d4efc","tid":1766063,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T10:06:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E5%8F%A4%E5%BE%B7%E6%98%8E/daily/article/20191202/20817099/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E5%258F%25A4%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E6%2598%258E%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191202%2F20817099%2F&d=r4%2BjDf%2BCRrsm4RwUuvkwRcorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=65229c6e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E5%258F%25A4%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E6%2598%258E%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191202%2F20817099%2F&h=c810b84d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E5%8F%A4%E5%BE%B7%E6%98%8E/daily/article/20191202/20817099/</a><br />\n<br />\n黑警戰術更進一步 - 古德明<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191202/large/1575185197_122c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191202%2Flarge%2F1575185197_122c.jpg&h=49d44b77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n十一月十一日，葵芳有黑警恨反暴政市民堵塞道路，駕摩托車加速向人多處撞去，來回三次，傷至少兩人，社會譁然。黑警當日說那隻同袍已即時休假，事件會「嚴肅調查」；偽行政長官鄭月娥也說「事件嚴重」，會秉公辦理云云。<br />\n<br />\n其實那隻黑警應怎樣辦理，有先例可援。十月六日，一的士司機恨反暴政者遊行，開車向人多處撞去，傷三人，一人更撞至兩腿骨折，黑警拘捕的不是那司機，而是被撞傷者。幸而在場市民先已把那司機秉公辦理，處以皮肉之刑，否則香港更見無法無天。事後，中共旗下守護香港大聯盟還許那司機以五十二萬元獎賞。那隻摩托車黑警一定是認為前車可鑑，誓復蹈血轍。<br />\n<br />\n而黑警「嚴肅調查」之後，戰術上顯然大有啟發，十一月十九日，開小巴到油麻地，也是加速向人多處撞去，反暴政者紛紛走避，黑警大獲全勝，高級黑警司汪威遜還得意洋洋說：「警方用了最合適的戰術，驅散暴徒，絕對不是草菅人命。」<br />\n<br />\n所以，那隻摩托車黑警戰術擘劃有功，已由開車襲人變成「遇襲受傷」，即時休假也變成「放病假」。鄭月娥還應頒以好警察一等獎。德國記者倫策（Enno Lenze）說：「我曾在伊斯蘭國戰線採訪，但香港警察比伊斯蘭國恐怖分子更加可怕：他們行動完全無規矩可循。」對黑警而言 ，這絕對不是過譽。 <br />\n<br />\n古德明<br />\n電郵 :appledailykoo@gmail.com"},{"pid":"08b134429c019d7403ca490ec5d2cfb4af055ef8","tid":1766063,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T10:15:45.000Z","msg":"CLS <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f46a3af9f782fab4b0cee8a53be1dfc2ab87bf8","tid":1766063,"uid":69544,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T10:19:31.000Z","msg":"所以絕對唔好因為黑警嘅一時放水，<br />\n就覺得佢地係好人。"},{"pid":"4fdffd4c18d9888c1803ed513067a3a24a29e2d9","tid":1766063,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T10:20:03.000Z","msg":"原來伊斯蘭國都有規矩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4da9c063d4bc933f1824e28c68e10567ac883aa0","tid":1766063,"uid":58209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T10:25:26.000Z","msg":"總係成日有人以為黑警係流四<br />\n大佬呀人地佢地日操夜操<br />\n學既全部都係打暴動既技巧<br />\n戰術唔贏你 體能都贏你啦<br />\n收你兩皮幾一個月唔通真係鳩流流咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a6c1b760e021c61326e9b28daf2e4accff3148e","tid":1766063,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T10:32:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30f379e5eb5d4a4c5b605f3faeda368d20d19453","tid":1766063,"uid":271123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4fdffd4c18d9888c1803ed513067a3a24a29e2d9","tid":1766063,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T10:20:03.000Z","msg":"原來伊斯蘭國都有規矩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"reply